<subSubSection pageId="137" pageNumber="138" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="137.[151,1436,764,968]" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,496,871,896]" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Distribution and habitat.</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[502,646,871,896]" country="Papua New Guinea" name="New Ireland" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">New Ireland</collectingRegion>
: 1, 2.—General distribution: 
<collectingCountry box="[971,1080,871,896]" name="Indonesia" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Indonesia</collectingCountry>
east to 
<collectingCountry box="[1165,1230,871,896]" name="Palau" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Palau</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1241,1285,872,895]" country="Micronesia" name="Yap" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Yap</collectingRegion>
(
<collectingCountry box="[1299,1429,871,896]" name="Micronesia" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Micronesia</collectingCountry>
) and 
<collectingCountry box="[198,389,908,933]" name="Solomon Islands" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Solomon Islands</collectingCountry>
, north to 
<collectingCountry box="[495,625,908,933]" name="Philippines" pageId="137" pageNumber="138">Philippines</collectingCountry>
. Solitary, nocturnal, found in mangrove habitats including estuaries, and in coastal reefs, 
<quantity box="[333,418,944,968]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="0.0" pageId="137" pageNumber="138" unit="m" value="15.0" valueMax="30.0" valueMin="0.0">0–30 m</quantity>
